<! [CDATA[
SK Hynix Logo
SK hynix Inc. is a South Korean memory semiconductor supplier of dynamic random-access memory chips and flash memory chips. Hynix is the world’s second-largest memory chipmaker and the world’s 3rd-largest semiconductor company. Founded as Hyundai Electronic Industrial Co., Ltd. in 1983 and known as Hyundai Electronics, the company has manufacturing sites in Korea, the United States, China and Taiwan. In 2012, when SK Telecom became its major shareholder, Hynix merged to SK Group.
You can download theSK Hynixlogo on full-version of the page.
